2. On the date which is three years from the date on which Part 6 of the 
Assisted Decision-Making (Capacity) Act 2015 enters into force, the following 
provisions shall be deleted from the Rules of the Superior Courts: 

(a) Order 67; 

(b) Order 70A, rule 26(2); 

(c) Order 79, rule 26 (as substituted by these Rules); 

(d) Order 117A, rule 4(c); 

(e) Order 134A, rules 14(1) and (2); 

(f) Appendix K, Forms 1 to 18 inclusive.
